DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to investigate the comorbidities of lower urinary tract symptoms or pelvic organ prolapse in a nationwide population-based data in Taiwan during the study period of 2001-2010, a total of 10 years.
DOC.brief_title: Population-based Estimates of Medical Comorbidities in Women With Lower Urinary Tract Symptoms or Pelvic Organ Prolapse
DOC.criteria: all cases with lower urinary tract symptoms
